description: Grand Tours of Scotland Series 1 Travel Documentary hosted by Paul Murton, published by BBC in 2010 - English narration. http://docuwiki.net/images/c/ca/Grand-Tours-of-Scotland-Series-1-Cover.jpg Information ------------------------------ Paul Murton follows in the footsteps of the first tourists to Scotland.
